MoD published the Aerodrome Manual on their website . 
  The information could be used as 'an invasion guide' by Argentina . 
  It has the exact GPS co-ordinates of Mount Pleasant aerodrome on the Falklands Islands . 
  The base is home to four RAF Typhoon aircraft tasked with defending the islands . 
  The MoD accidentally published the details of the base on the website . 
  Argentina is preparing to lease 12 long-range bombers from Russia . 
  MoD admitted the manual could be downloaded by anyone but denied it was sensitive . 
 